The Mexican Institute of the social security (IMSS) announced that directs an investigation to discover the gene of the obesity in children and young, called protocol 'Genetic of the obesity of the infancy and the adolescence', that will permit to include associated scoreboards to the excess.
In a communiqué, the leader of the Unit of Medical Investigation in Biochemist of the Hospital of Specialties of the hospital National 21st century, Miguel Cross López, explained that a multidisciplinary team of doctors was integrated, nurses, nutriólogos and social workers.
Said team is supported by specialists and students of graduate of the National Institute of Public Health (INSP) and of the Center of Investigation and of Studies Advanced (Cinvestav) of the National Technical Institute (IPN).
