Once comply the objective to meet to 500 or 600 smaller, the study will continue in the Unit Sports Independence (south of the Federal District) and finally in the Sports Unit Dwell them (to the north of the Federal District).
It explained that the purpose of this investigation is to know the components and the importance of the genetics with regard to the development of the obesity and to identify in children and Mexican youths factors of risk to prevent the apparition of degenerative chronic illnesses.
Upon being celebrated this 14 from November the World Day of the Diabetes, needed that the objective is to meet three thousand children and youths between six and 14 years of age, with the consent and supervision of its parents, for the application of specific questionnaires on diet.
Also he will be asked him on the preceding and physical activity heredofamiliares of illnesses, for the purpose of avoiding factors of risk that unchain sufferings as diabetes or kidney failure.
It detailed that Saturdays applies to all the participating measurements antropométricas (weight, size, circumference of waist), takes of arterial pressure, decision of the levels of glucose, triglicéridos, cholesterol and insulin and genetic (is sought to identify genes that associate to the childlike obesity).
Cross López indicated that this investigation obeys to the worry of the professionals of the health by the alarming increase of weight in the smaller.
'The surveys of health of 1999 and 2006 indicated that in so alone six years there was an increment, in the case of the children, of 77 percent in obesity, and of the girls of 47 percent; in terms of excess also a dramatic ascent was observed', emphasized the specialist of the IMSS.
It indicated that the justification for the search of the scoreboards is supported in which the population of the country differs of other by its genetic history.
It reported that on the average, the Mexican considers 65 hundred of inheritance Native American, 30 percent European and five percent African and this condition he reflects in the genes that associate to diabetes and excess of weight.
It explained that in a general way, the genetics of the obesity is translated in the incapacity to burn the excess of energy that consume (calories) and that is stored in the shape of grease.
