Thus it was the work of the caleño that identified the corpse of Alfonso Gray
A lofoscopista of Cali passed to the history as the man that confirmed the death of "Alfonso Gray".
The work of these officials is key.
Last November 4 a lofoscopista of the CTI of Cali passed to the history as the man that confirmed the identity of the leader of the Farc: "Alfonso Gray", through the comparison of its fingerprints.
Of the seven lofoscopistas that labor in the sectional one of the CTI, that week touched the shift of "availability" to Eliazar González, a Roof Port man that carries 21 years working in the area of judicial investigation.
Upon initiating their career, González worked in municipalities of the Collided, where many times had to be gone for more than five days in the forest to arrive at the place in which were the corpses that should be identifying.
In the 2000 it was transferred to the capital of the Valley and, after carrying out the corresponding courses, specialized itself in lofoscopia, that is the study of the skin of friction, that is to say, of the palms of the hands and of the feet.
The week of the operating one against you ally Alfonso Gray to Eliazar they notified him that carried most minimum clothes for three days.
Somewhat large he expected him.
Friday in the night left for the Cauca in a helicopter from Palmira.
It knew that should identify two corpses and that suspected that one of them was of the man that directed to the oldest guerrilla warfare of the world, for which they asked him that carried the card decadactilar of Guillermo Lion Sáenz (its true name).
Nevertheless, when it arrived with the team of investigation to the place in which the corpse was found did not recognize it for its physical aspect, therefore was very different to which had seen in the mass media.
Was without beard, dress like a peasant of the zone, without eyeglasses and a lot more thin.
But the tracks do not lie.
It accompanied by a magnifier galtoniana, ink, a transplantador and a flashlight, Eliazar compared the finger impressions of the corpse with those of the card.
Its eye did not fail him: was "Alfonso Gray".
That same night, the native man of Port Roof was the responsible for confirming him the minister of Defense, Juan Carlos Finch, that yes was a matter of the leader of the Farc.
In search of the track
For a dactiloscopista of the Sijín of Cali the recognition that did the president Juan Manuel Holy to Eliazar González, in the press conference by the operating one against "Gray", he is very significant.
Many people does not he know our work.
The dactiloscopia is an exact science, without margin of error, that can come be key in the resolution of crimes.
Aside from the identification of corpses, the lofoscopistas support investigations by crimes as theft and homicide and they confirm the identity of the people captured.
When they are captured, many delinquents present false decrees or do not have roles.
We take them the finger impression and we seek them in the database.
The investigator related that, in a case of theft, he touched him to remove a piece of wall of a house, therefore in that place the thief had supported his hand to remove a full strong box of jewels and money.
"The walls are difficult because are not appropriate surfaces to remove a finger impression, but in that case we could obtain the track of all the hand and to identify the delinquent, that had participated in different thefts", recalled.
The tracks can also rule out or to reaffirm suspects in cases of homicide.
It does little they found a dead man, with bottles of liquor around him.
Through the investigation was determined that a relative could be a suspect of the crime and, really, a track in the bottle coincided.
Although this does not it guarantee that have been the murderer, yes locates it in the scene of the crime.
A dactiloscopista of the CTI explained that in the objects "the tracks are removed with chemical or physical reagents".
