To solve the equation of the nuclear energy, one must admit that not a miraculous source of production of electricity exists, just like neither a diabolic source exists.
The development on the part of Areva of solutions with low emissions of CO2, nuclear and renewable, shows the complementary character of the sources of energy.
In the case of the nuclear energy, turns out to be indispensable to maintain the maximum level of security.
In France, we have an Authority of security that exercises a so much transparent and strict control on the existing head offices as on the construction of Flamanville.
Our teams, of recognized professionalism, they are also obsessed by the security.
In half century, the nuclear sector has suffered three serious accidents.
So alone one, that of Three Mile Island, was produced in some normal operating conditions; did not cause consequences neither for the people neither for the environment.
In Chernobil, the accident itself due to the design of the reactor and to some inexcusable human failures.
In Fukushima, some people seem to forget that the accident themselves due to two natural catastrophes of an unprecedented reach, that caused the death of scores of thousands of people.
The nuclear sector will learn of this accident, just as did it of the two previous.
